Petrobras to Sign Accord for Fertilizer Plant

-- B y   J e s s i c a   B r i c e
-- 
2011-03-17T18:43:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/petrobras-to-sign-accord-for-fertilizer-plant-correct-.html
  Petroleo Brasileiro SA (PETR4) , Brazil’s
state-controlled oil producer, plans to sign a memorandum of
understanding to build a $1.3 billion nitrogen-based fertilizer
plant in Brazil’s Minas Gerais state.  Petrobras, as the companies are known, will sign the accord
tomorrow, according to an e-mailed statement. Petrobras also
plans to study the construction of a pipeline with Cia.
Energetica de Minas Gerais.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jessica Brice in  Sao Paulo  at 
 jbrice1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
